{"tid":879921,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"25歲中國女子在日本被殺 室友承認“用菜刀砍人”","createTime":"2018-10-28T11:17:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-28T14:37:25.000Z","uid":184679,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"ef5d0992830ebca8a401ae5d028e9b78d441e374","tid":879921,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T11:17:46.000Z","msg":"當地時間27日上午11點半左右，日本群馬縣伊勢崎市一公寓內，中國籍技能實習生、25歲的李雪被發現頭部流血，送醫後死亡。警方調查後，於28日淩晨以涉嫌殺人，逮捕了其同是中國籍技能實習生室友，30歲的劉某某。劉承認殺人，稱&ldquo;因生活的事被警告，無法忍耐&rdquo;，她還承認是&ldquo;用菜刀砍了人&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n　　據共同社報道，在日本群馬縣伊勢崎市曲澤町一公寓二樓的一個房間裡，附近居民撥打119稱發現&ldquo;有女性流血倒地&rdquo;。住在該房間的中國技能實習生李雪被發現頭部流血倒在浴室內，被送醫後死亡。<br />\n<br />\n　　從遺體情況等來看，該縣警方早前認為很可能是殺人事件，并向同住的兩名中國籍女性聽取情況。警方稱，附近居民因聽到房間裡傳出女性的哭泣聲而感到奇怪，抵達後發現李雪穿著衣服倒在地上。據悉，李雪與同住的兩人都在伊勢崎市某生產廠工作。<br />\n<br />\n　　據悉，現場位於JR兩毛線國定站以北約3公裏處，附近散布著住宅與田地。<br />\n<br />\n　　1980年代初，&ldquo;外國人研修制度&rdquo;在日本設立，至今已走過三十多年的歷程，中國一直是日本研修生的最大來源國。1993年，日政府在研修生接收制度的基礎上，設立了技能實習生制度，并隨後進行了多次修改。根據現行的制度，前往日本的務工人員在經過一個月的研修生過渡後，便轉為技能實習生，大部分是三年期合同，而且合同期間原則上不能中途回國。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.hkcna.hk/content/2018/1028/718778.shtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcna.hk%2Fcontent%2F2018%2F1028%2F718778.shtml&d=xEmi5%2B9VA00o%2BtFVGKwxAcPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=d3248774\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hkcna.hk/content/2018/1028/718778.shtml</a>"},{"pid":"9589805b6110696d447e77fef3f562c513a9e0fe","tid":879921,"uid":198583,"like":1,"dislike":12,"score":-11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T11:18:25.000Z","msg":"日本鬼子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9e2854f57197e9ab6093628a6a95920a2d191f5","tid":879921,"uid":52942,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"quote":{"pid":"9589805b6110696d447e77fef3f562c513a9e0fe","tid":879921,"uid":198583,"like":1,"dislike":12,"score":-11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T11:18:25.000Z","msg":"日本鬼子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T11:19:44.000Z","msg":"犯人都係中國人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b5c162d437d36601e0dbceb6fae74b6523d3e1c","tid":879921,"uid":174017,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T11:20:53.000Z","msg":"話知你係支那同袍 條氣唔順照殺"},{"pid":"290c8db63905ee5c071295763c54cb12c8b7952e","tid":879921,"uid":54777,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T11:21:03.000Z","msg":"稱&ldquo;因生活的事被警告，無法忍耐&rdquo;<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0cc81380abc08c88b65a0f23cb78efff1afa8e5","tid":879921,"uid":98386,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T12:15:29.000Z","msg":"狗咬狗骨<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cd76c8f5d40af45d5e721f6a0bde6a73bdc8303","tid":879921,"uid":70786,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T13:42:08.000Z","msg":"五毛:感謝日本為中國人提供宣洩平台,維護中日友好共存共榮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5da3b0ed2f7991408c30fae939e4ae78cd380ae","tid":879921,"uid":191762,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c9e2854f57197e9ab6093628a6a95920a2d191f5","tid":879921,"uid":52942,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"quote":{"pid":"9589805b6110696d447e77fef3f562c513a9e0fe","tid":879921,"uid":198583,"like":1,"dislike":12,"score":-11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T11:18:25.000Z","msg":"日本鬼子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T11:19:44.000Z","msg":"犯人都係中國人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T13:43:56.000Z","msg":"好多中國人係外國遇害都係俾中國人害"},{"pid":"e253e6ee4f3b90d2d5f053eae1b73fb91b51f85d","tid":879921,"uid":24345,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T13:50:31.000Z","msg":"第幾單喺日本嘅中國人殺中國人事件<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 之